{
  "stem": "22047.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in-- in '42, as I said, moved to Van Nuys, or Sherman Oaks, and I went to Van Nuys high school in '41 or '42. '41.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "September of '41, graduated in '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was involved in that and not specifically in any war effort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was a professor of military science and tactics at three high schools in the Los Angeles area; Hollywood High School, Fremont High School, and Van Nuys.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I think I told you the story of my experience with him at Van Nuys, because he was the boss there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- when he was an umpire, during the maneuvers up in Washington, he had to go up there, and he was gone for a significant period of time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when he was there, we went to-- my mother and sister and I went to Portland and stayed with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so he was in Fort Lewis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- when I went to UCLA, I was in the ROTC at UCLA.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our whole unit was called in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was sort of being drafted and sort of enlisted, because I was involved in ROTC.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was kind of-- kind of a given that our unit was going to be taken into basic training as a unit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to Camp Roberts, California, north of Santa Barbara and south of Moterey, here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I spent my basic training months there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was in May of '43, having been inducted, actually, at Fort MacArthur in San Pedro.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spent from May until September, I guess it was, in basic training, and then I stayed on as a cadre man at Camp Roberts.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got promoted to colonel-- or corporal.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
